        {
            "id": 5898406,
            "title": "滙豐控股(005)昨在港斥2.5億元回購298萬股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》滙豐控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00005:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00005\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00005-HK</a>)公布,昨日在香港聯交所回購298.04萬股,每股價格介乎83.95元至85.1元,每股加權平均價約84.477元,涉資約2.52億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　與此同時,滙控於英國回購236.05萬股,每股介乎8.439至8.518<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/gbpusd\">英鎊</a>,加權平均價為8.4804<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/gbpusd\">英鎊</a>,涉資2001.83萬<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/gbpusd\">英鎊</a>。自2月20日開始回購以來,滙控已回購合共約7891.63萬股普通股,總代價約8.989億美元。(eh)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5898406",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 08:53:00",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 5898400,
            "title": "《盤前攻略》美股靠穩惟道指仍弱勢,恒指料窄幅波動關注業績期",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》美國2月消費物價指數(CPI)按年2.8%,低預期升2.9%,亦低於1月的3%,按月增幅由0.5%放緩至0.2%,為4個月來最慢升幅,低過預期增0.3%;期內扣除食品和能源的核心CPI按年增幅降至3.1%,小過預期升3.2%,按月漲0.2%,亦低過預期。投資者趁低吸納科技股,納指周三反彈212點或1.2%,收報17648點;標普500指數高收27點或0.5%,收報5599點;<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道指</a>則仍跌82點或0.2%,收報41350點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　美國總統特朗普帶頭購買特斯拉新車,加上摩根士丹利建議逢低買入特斯拉股票後,特斯拉股價延續升勢,收市再升近8%。台積電有意與英偉達等成立合資公司,營運英特爾代工工廠,英偉達升逾6%,英特爾升約5%,台積電升近4%。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數跌1.2%。阿里巴巴跌1.35%,報137.14美元;京東跌0.93%,報40.37美元;百度跌2.19%,報92.40美元;理想升0.81%,報29.73美元;小鵬跌6.11%,報24.73美元;百勝中國升0.45%,報49.33美元;嗶哩嗶哩跌6.50%,報21.29美元;蔚來跌2.30%,報5.10美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">*夜期略高水,ADR個別走*</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　恒指夜期跌6點,報23633,高水33點。ADR個股方面,美團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03690:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03690\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03690-HK</a>)ADR較港股低0.15%,折合168.0港元;長和(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00001:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00001\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00001-HK</a>)ADR較港股低</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">0.35%,折合49.2港元;騰訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00700:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00700\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00700-HK</a>)ADR較港股高0.65%,折合515.3港元;小米(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01810-HK</a>)ADR較港股高0.18%,折合52.1港元;港交所(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00388:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00388\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00388-HK</a>)ADR較港股高2.04%,折合356.5港元;滙控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00005:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00005\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00005-HK</a>)ADR較港股高1.83%,折合86.6港元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　*市場焦點轉移至業績表現*</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　牛熊證街貨比例為61.5比38.5。目前熊證重貨區位於24700至24799區間,該區有789張對應期指;而最多新增區位於24000至24099區間,該區總數775張中有559張屬於新增,顯示淡友有信心恒指難破二萬四。而牛證重貨區位於23200至23299區間,該區有1187張對應期指,最多新增區位於23300至23399區間,該區全部230張皆為新增。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　有「黑期」之稱的新加坡HS50指數現升30點,報23601,預料恒指接近平開。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">近日美股走勢波動,儘管恒指連續兩日盤中低位均曾跌四、五百點,但收市跌幅都大幅收窄,顯示港股仍有一定支撐。但由於現時處於業績公布期,市場焦點或轉移至業績表現。預料恒指維持在10天線(約23596)附近窄幅上落。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　今日有多家大企業公布業績,包括東方海外(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00316:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00316\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00316-HK</a>)、九倉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00004:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00004\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00004-HK</a>)、太古A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00019:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00019\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00019-HK</a>)、太古B(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00087:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00087\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00087-HK</a>)、太古地產(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01972:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01972\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01972-HK</a>)、白雲山(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00874:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00874\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00874-HK</a>)和微博(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09898:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09898\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09898-HK</a>)等,請密切關注。(vs)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
