        {
            "id": 5898389,
            "title": "外資近3日買超個股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 外資累計買超 3 日的股票<br/>華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>)、復華台灣科技優息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00929:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00929\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00929-TW</a>)、玉山金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2884:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2884\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2884-TW</a>)、廣宇 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2328:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2328\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2328-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 外資累計買超 2 日的股票<br/>華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、復華台灣科技優息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00929:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00929\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00929